PrecisAuthority to execute an AGREEMENT with the RURAL MUNICIPALITY OF ROCKWOOD which provides for the leasing to the aforementioned, for a term of twenty- five (25) years, of some 19.82 hectares of vacant land situated on the grounds of STONY MOUNTAIN PENITENTIARY in the Village of Stony Mountain, Manitoba, for the purposes of a sewage lagoon.
